{"tid":2419493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"終於發現夏朝文字？原來搞錯考古人員嘅水筆記號 國家級研究所致歉","createTime":"2021-02-23T10:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:23:56.000Z","uid":63183,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7747bb4a32b9f0d599e50279c70133fab50285","tid":2419493,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXAUXMD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXAUXMD.png&h=2dfa2a5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5392&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv352AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=95bd95f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5392</a><br />\n中國一直聲稱有「五千年文明」，但商朝之前嘅所謂「夏朝」已經搵唔到任何文字，談何文明。因此尋找夏朝文字一直被列為國家級任務，但發掘多年都未有成果。<br />\n<br />\n近日（17號），中国學者李維明發表《二里頭遺址祭祀陶文初識》一文，話喺2000年二里頭遺址掘出嚟嘅陶片發現有「文字」，仲可解讀為「在土用蛇、六（條或次）舉行告祭」。<br />\n<br />\n但一日之後，考古隊就出文致歉，話呢啲「文字」其實係用黑色筆寫嘅考古編號「00ⅢT1H22」。佢哋承認「早年整理資料過程中，確有不規範之處，對大家使用資料進行研究時，造成誤解，對此深表歉意。」但都堅持會喺二里頭搵到文字：「李先生認為二里頭文化存在文字，我們贊同這一觀點，將在今後的田野考古工作中更加關注有關細節」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20210221/photo/0221-00178-015b2.jpg?resize=540%2C696&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20210221%2Fphoto%2F0221-00178-015b2.jpg%3Fresize%3D540%252C696%26ssl%3D1&h=028a3509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶片上面的確係有文字，不過係考古隊人員寫落嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20210221/photo/0221-00178-015b1.jpg?resize=540%2C722&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20210221%2Fphoto%2F0221-00178-015b1.jpg%3Fresize%3D540%252C722%26ssl%3D1&h=a0cd672b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李維明認為文字應該係古代蛇嘅象徵。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒亦都指李維明有唔着，未睇過實物，淨係睇相就喺到判斷古字迹。睇返資料，李維明的確係古字專家，有歷史學博士，曾經做過中國國家博物館原學術研究中心副主任，研究館員，2003年喺商代牛肋骨嘅刻辭上，發現第11個殘存文字。<br />\n<br />\n二里頭遺址喺發現頭廿幾年裏，學界普遍認為係商都，但近三四十年就「達成共識」係夏都。喺入邊都掘到好多銅器同玉器。不過，喺呢啲器具上都未係好似商朝搵到甲骨文咁，搵到當時嘅文字去證明真係屬於另一個朝代。<br />\n<br />\n今次被大陸傳媒形容為「考古界最大的烏龍事件」。有網民表示，學術應該嚴謹，「誰都會有錯誤，但這事有損學術界公信力，貽笑大方」。"},{"pid":"733a736a885640a08a5c68044f0ddb34881a39a0","tid":2419493,"uid":224066,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkizdm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frkizdm2.png&h=d1a664c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"243dab8efe2f289a0b451c9427c6ee3c2596d46d","tid":2419493,"uid":185651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab519bdcad9e166c8acf23114b71ac9491625af0","tid":2419493,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2060e83fef5d98a03dc3cb74ea051923540f152f","tid":2419493,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"屌佢連啲字都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f8b8a81beb3c16de8e3f26ac924eb7e6e17558","tid":2419493,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733a736a885640a08a5c68044f0ddb34881a39a0","tid":2419493,"uid":224066,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkizdm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frkizdm2.png&h=d1a664c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"又可以係 貪，奸淫擄掠，支那國粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c6131fbe5528465b2a033afb7937a6b78f8600","tid":2419493,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"夏朝已有阿拉伯數字及英文字母，證明中東及歐美都係中國固有領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2285ba3d8d8ae490541ea3d43e100cbc49428bf2","tid":2419493,"uid":44454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"點解唔調返轉,證明夏朝已經有箱頭筆？"},{"pid":"303ea00936ad9df7ae6ba60b39eed3ccd93077a7","tid":2419493,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591892fef75233adfe88259da0b2afe307579cfa","tid":2419493,"uid":372844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"有冇考古巴，直接係件野到做記號條咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a305250bfa28bfe540bab75b6d6da64d1b309e","tid":2419493,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"仲話專家, 連字都唔識多個, 搞邊科<br />\n應該一死以謝天下"},{"pid":"2aa1bd4a18f5ea8bfc97e875eb1cb264c8710715","tid":2419493,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"癲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f422e87d8e623394d6035af424822d315d6ededd","tid":2419493,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"&gt;<em>搵唔到任何文字，談何文明</em><br />\n<br />\n印加都冇文字，一樣當佢係文明<br />\n<br />\n其實點先叫做「文明」係冇硬性標準"}]}